high_descs: turn left around the counter top, then go straight to the oven stove top
pick up the knife with the yellow handle to the left of the stove top
slice the bread to the left of the white bowl
turn around, go straight towards the wall, then turn left to face the refrigerator
open the refrigerator, then place the knife down on the bottom right shelf
close the door, then return to the counter top near the stove top
pick up a slice of bread from the counter top
return to the refrigerator with the slice of bread
open the refrigerator door, then place the bread on the top left shelf, then close the door for several seconds before taking the slice out
turn left, then go straight to the microwave
place the slice of bread in the microwave, then shut the door
anns.task_desc: Slice bread and cool it in the refrigerator so it can be warmed in the microwave

high_descs: Turn around and move around the counter to the stove on the left.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Slice the bread to your left.
Turn around and move to the fridge on the left.
Put the knife in the fridge.
Turn around and move to the stove on the right.
Pick up a slice of bread from the counter.
Turn around and move to the fridge on the left.
Chill the slice of bread in the freezer and take it out again.
Turn to the left and move to the microwave.
Place the slice of bread into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Prepare a slice of chilled bread and put it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white stove on the left.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle in between the gold pepper grinders on the counter.
Slice the loaf of bread to the left of the clear container on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the white fridge on the left.
Put the knife inside the fridge on the bottom shelf to chill and close the doors.
Turn around and walk to the stove on the right.
Pick up a slice of bread from the loaf on the left side of the counter.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on the left.
Open the fridge, put the slice of bread on the top left shelf, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the microwave on the counter ahead.
Put the chilled slice of bread in the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Chill a knife and place a slice of chilled bread in a microwave.
